Screen Open 0,640,256,2,$8000
Curs Off : Flash Off : Cls 0
Palette $0,$FFF
Double Buffer : Autoback 0
'
Wb 3d Centre 320,128
Wb 3d Eye 0,0,400
AX=45 : AY=0 : AZ=0
Wb 3d Angle AX,AY,AZ
'
While Mouse Key=0
Add AX,3,0 To 359
Add AY,3,0 To 359
Add AZ,3,0 To 359
Wb 3d Angle AX,AY,AZ
'
Wb 3d Locate -100,-100,0
X=Wb 3d X : Y=Wb 3d Y
Wb 3d Draw 100,-100,0
Wb 3d Draw 100,100,0
Wb 3d Draw -100,100,0
Draw To X,Y
'
Wb 3d Locate -75,-75,20
X=Wb 3d X : Y=Wb 3d Y
Wb 3d Draw 75,-75,20
Wb 3d Draw 75,75,20
Wb 3d Draw -75,75,20
Draw To X,Y
'
Wb 3d Locate -75,-75,-20
X=Wb 3d X : Y=Wb 3d Y
Wb 3d Draw 75,-75,-20
Wb 3d Draw 75,75,-20
Wb 3d Draw -75,75,-20
Draw To X,Y
'
Circle 320,128,20
Locate 0,0 : Print Timer
Timer=0
Screen Swap 
Wait Vbl 
Cls 0
Wend 
